{"tid":1113112,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼市雙雄如何留得住","createTime":"2019-04-17T19:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T03:52:47.000Z","uid":392,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fa638454e917a68bd190afdf9002efad321df6","tid":1113112,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T19:12:33.000Z","msg":"晉級歐聯原來殊不易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916ddb04c33ce54164430ac2ec44e949434628ba","tid":1113112,"uid":392,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:56:36.000Z","msg":"為了專心英超的賽事 <br />\n退出歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fb8d9426aef7fd57a64723d7119e401928fd59","tid":1113112,"uid":247905,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:56:57.000Z","msg":"就不必打美斯"},{"pid":"5ae676f5169c0a18b541306a2f2ceff42be14d8d","tid":1113112,"uid":13106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:57:22.000Z","msg":"誰曾話報仇魯營太輕易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aec05018fd6611b038e3c7849bede9b86b0075","tid":1113112,"uid":96650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:08:39.000Z","msg":"就不必打美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73920912170b17ff6d73460fd08203d6c9b5b366","tid":1113112,"uid":114328,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:09:32.000Z","msg":"歐洲的賽事 重頭開始 霸氣杯那時 <br />\n輸波兩個字 成為往事 再買不太遲 <br />\n陪伴隔離阿積士 期待市內再打比三次 <br />\n英超的冠軍 英超的亞軍 <br />\n徘徊在富咸伯明瀚左近<br />\n車仔跟阿妓 各佔一地 你卻收了皮 <br />\n輸給巴素利 和拿玻里 那半粒馬鼻 <br />\n成日掛住八比二 成日掛住那打比一次 <br />\nMU都吃屎 Cty都吃屎  <br />\n誰曾話報仇魯營太輕易<br />\n曼市雙雄如何留得住 <br />\n晉級歐聯原來殊不易 <br />\n為了專心英超的賽事 <br />\n退出歐聯 就不必打美斯<br />\n高級的競技 連場失利 最厚薪朗尼 <br />\n當天的基治 和拿斯利 再見返托尼 <br />\n其實最是有星味 仍舊領銜了英超big四 <br />\n摩佬都報喜 哥帥都報喜 <br />\n然而曼市內卻唯有腥味<br />\n曼市雙雄如何留得住 <br />\n晉級歐聯原來殊不易 <br />\n就算千千億億的赤字 <br />\n轉會當時 又不懂揀幼齒<br />\n但柏天尼如何留得住 <br />\n熱刺篤城原來捱不住 <br />\n為了修補英超的聲譽 <br />\n退出歐聯 做歐洲的霸主<br />\n<br />\n中撚哂"},{"pid":"fc71cfa85bdba3b11d2378a8545a8a71746f2860","tid":1113112,"uid":114328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:25:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=of96cjoe-Ec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dof96cjoe-Ec&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=7c4492e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=of96cjoe-Ec</a>"},{"pid":"525d460c6281d68c76694179e84fd981f17fa679","tid":1113112,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:26:24.000Z","msg":"冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86c8f4438393fe6ffe75a72a87ca75201474fe7","tid":1113112,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13023b9a370600ca960e6576948a444bc9f09d0d","tid":1113112,"uid":1560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d7920151dad3ec1849197bfbec2ec85938b124","tid":1113112,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"以前就陪伴隔離阿積士<br />\n人地而家準備入決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a970f0e33fb94417420627d6a2786802cb44da","tid":1113112,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"熱刺篤城捱得住啊"}]}